HEADWORD: Outgrowth
<hw>Out"growth`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>That which grows
out of, or proceeds from, anything; an excrescence; an offshoot; hence,
a result or consequence.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

